Japan Tobacco Says Government Should Be Cautious on Tax Increase

-- B y   S h u n i c h i   O z a s a
-- 
2011-09-20T05:34:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/japan-tobacco-says-government-should-be-cautious-on-tax-increase.html
Japan  should be cautious about
raising cigarette taxes and should not count on tobacco as a
major source of revenue, Japan Tobacco Executive Deputy
President Masakazu Shimizu told reporters today in Tokyo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
